results.name: Decimal expansion of Integral_{x=0..1} Product_{k>=1} (1-x^(24*k)) dx.
comment: Equals the value of the Dirichlet L-series of a non-principal character modulo 12 (A110161) at s=2. - _Jianing Song_, Nov 16 2019
link: M. W. Coffey, Summatory relations and prime products for the Stieltjes constants and other related results, arXiv:1701.07064, eq. (2.1)
formula: Equals Sum_{k>=1} A110161(n)/k^2 = Sum_{k>=1} Kronecker(12,k)/k^2. - _Jianing Song_, Nov 16 2019
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, May 29 2015
